<p><a name="Early_economic_thought" id="Early_economic_thought"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=History_of_economic_thought&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Early economic thought">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Early economic thought</span></h2>
<table style="margin: 0 0 1em 1em; border: 1px solid #aaaaaa; clear: both" align="right" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr>
<td style="background:#BBDDFF; padding: 3px 5px 3px 5px;" align="center"><b><a href="/wiki/History_of_science" title="History of science">History of science</a></b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<div class="center">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:Libr0310.jpg" class="image" title="Libr0310.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/24/Libr0310.jpg/120px-Libr0310.jpg" width="120" height="183" border="0" /></a></div>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="background:#b0c4de; font-size: 95%; border-top: 1px solid #aaaaaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaaaaa; padding: 0 5px 0 5px;">Background</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="font-size: 90%; padding: 0 5px 0 5px; background: #edf3fe;"><a href="/wiki/Theories_and_sociology_of_the_history_of_science" title="Theories and sociology of the history of science">Theories/sociology</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
